headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Strategic Services Group, Inc.
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Rochester Hills, Michigan-based Strategic Services Group, Inc. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
